The paper focuses on a dataset collected by an autonomous vehicle platform, which includes annotated data from cameras, Lidar, and a GNSS+INS system. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions that Lidar frame annotations have been provided for 3D object detection and tracking, which suggests that the paper may also belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category.
